: ["5 a.m.–11 p.m."], "Saturday": ["5 a.m.–11:30 p.m."], "Sunday": ["5 a.m.–11 p.m."], "Thursday": ["5 a.m.–11 p.m."], "Tuesday": ["5 a.m.–11 p.m."], "Wednesday": ["5 a.m.–11 p.m."]}'::jsonb, '[{"Name": "Hoa Tran", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWYZvEkBrBdk69UXKsSLBG0krpH22WUKQkIDsifdHV0H-0CoHw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "I’m very happy learning tennis here! The court is clean, spacious, and in excellent condition. The coach is extremely dedicated, patient, and explains techniques in a very easy-to-understand way. I’ve made noticeable progress after just a few sessions. Highly recommended!", "Images": ["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn30n-_OTDrsPYZMscw1BcHf-2IL98fCqV29uYoLeWDf7xv5FQzuwHWqkMHOt8xrP-n38UDqFA2mQ1Vvh5S9zUB8j3xUNxjtUh-yFeSHDoscg5J2UKGS28v0o1zXLW5ntJDHip6rrQ629_c5=k-no", "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2GYTlieh7LmfUHCc6vSzoWgx_J5gTT3YQJiY6mXL7eCdeU2l3zVN3-nEYV9pB1sWkgxorQ1gaSb5icafsesSmTaAi4GYz81Z72AJqcduHMPs0t4iay8Ud1iWLDkp0M6R9dhXBNJB7ozQ0f=k-no"], "When": "2025-6-17"}, {"Name": "Alexis Guyon", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXqiGS_8mZY_fYDccJ55r4JOslyVPzRv9hOn7VVbPu8utkW89xL=s120-c-rp-mo-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "Amazing coach! I recommend him to anyone who wants to play and learn tennis in Da Nang. I trained with him for two months and learned a lot.", "Images": ["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3-CpbeSMFlOMScKk5U8gnQ9KbHhPPOJp2KFnAJDHPpL2QYp8JAsx8tgTnhIOrT1JwAOdO5eJHUJK4iksV7fZ0FL8Pn9b-RbxAK62SxkyBonYT97Kn3EUoClpJM8IAV0olwUlHnDQ=k-no"], "When": "2025-5-14"}, {"Name": "Avery Kim", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIZCvjxzMInu4AXIax4YmFR3lzshzt7jTJ2ttB3tDP8Q8O02Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "I had great sessions with the coach during my stay. Highly recommend!", "Images": null, "When": ""}, {"Name": "дмитрий богданов", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleuserco