nd price increase.... seems lower quality courts and higher price. Need to find a new favorite court :(", "Images": null, "When": ""}, {"Name": "Liubov Denisenko", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWPiNJbDeKSp_h60K6md9SMQ3LmjESHrGZMsVCQXuh9yvRRdlux=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100", "Rating": 3, "Description": "Отличная удобная закрытая площадка для игры в пиклбол. Чисто. Все новое. Большие хорошие вентиляторы. Но больше не вернусь сюда. И снимаю две звезды за то, что игроки не относятся уважительно друг к другу и курят прям внутри. Я сюда приехала поиграть и позаниматься спортом, а не дышать сигаретным дымом. Абсолютно не понимаю, в чем проблема выйти на улицу и покурить. Это же не бар, это спортивная площадка", "Images": null, "When": ""}, {"Name": "Nguyễn Thu Phương", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUD9syUp_5YocxpCodXxaxZ2QxsruSldQ6dboVLz9PwAnrA1B1DlA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "Sân rộng, bề mặt sân đẹp, hai biên rộng dễ chạy, thi đấu hoặc học pickleball tại đây rất ổn", "Images": ["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0tJkhl9H6203mJlvbd4CLj6QEjv6kUeiMNpqG0x2SjMM7PiWks69s2CYQENQ3mggRKS2Eg31nQQk45dpjgPHyErUJvg_cmohxd7BuY39SLE0A5MXyQuETz5sa8pODwbxxCs03N=k-no"], "When": "2025-2-5"}, {"Name": "Vũ Hồ", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKGRUroVtj49_m67HDt8uviU1ajsqM3vlaWbkrgzE2X_ymauw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100", "Rating": 4, "Description": "Cũng ổn nhưng hơi ồn ào và nóng 😁", "Images": null, "When": ""}, {"Name": "HoaDo Villas", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX3kRKF9Ychr7kqyTHj8ssO7SWrLHcGONKg3kEyj5ivnrZjUxcX=s120-c-rp-mo-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "", "Images": null, "When": ""}, {"Name": "HẰNG VĂN THỊ THUÝ", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUWsZGq-64VYnPpdPTUwDGoGaNdSmz90WbKt8_7aIHK8pKRIa1O0A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "", "Images": null, "When": ""}, {"Name": "AirKidd Nick", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVozVZ7sxlSLJfQaYPvkif_k4exyhkNg_Ny_vyyezCeJoNUV94e=s120-c-rp-mo-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "", "Images": null, "When": ""}, {"Name": "Thành Đạt Nguyễn", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLM0f0ZMtn3GYfyiZylzCzvoXxZcLcFehj0aUqppvfQ0FBm_g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "", "Images": null, "When": ""}]'::jsonb, '{"Friday": {"10": 28, "11": 28, "12": 28, "13": 35, "14": 38, "15": 66, "16": 87, "17": 100, "18": 79, "19": 61, "20": 38, "21": 20, "22": 12, "4": 0, "5": 20, "6": 25, "7": 35, "8": 38, "9": 35}, "Monday": {"10": 15, "11": 10, "12": 7, "13": 17, "14": 30, "15": 48, "16": 69, "17": 69, "18": 66, "19": 43, "20": 30, "21": 15, "22": 17, "4": 0, "5": 25, "6": 23, "7": 33, "8": 30, "9": 25}, "Saturday": {"10": 25, "11": 23, "12": 12, "13": 10, "14": 17, "15": 41, "16": 58, "17": 74, "18": 61, "19": 41, "20": 30, "21": 30, "22": 35, "4": 0, "5": 30, "6": 38, "7": 46, "8": 38, "9": 38}, "Sunday": {"10": 15, "11": 15, "12": 17, "13": 25, "14": 33, "15": 35, "16": 33, "17": 30, "18": 28, "19": 30, "20": 38, "21": 33, "22": 28, "4": 0, "5": 15, "6": 20, "7": 12, "8": 10, "9": 10}, "Thursday": {"10": 25, "11": 23, "12": 28, "13": 20, "14": 33, "15": 43, "16": 53, "17": 66, "18": 58, "19": 61, "20": 51, "21": 41, "22": 23, "4": 0, "5": 20, "6": 23, "7": 23, "8": 20, "9": 15}, "Tuesday": {"10": 15, "11": 12, "12": 17, "13": 17, "14": 17, "15": 28, "16": 41, "17": 35, "18": 25, "19": 15, "20": 10, "21": 10, "22": 12, "4": 0, "5": 23, "6": 28, "7": 28, "8": 28, "9": 20}, "Wednesday": {"10": 12, "11": 20, "12": 23, "13": 35, "14": 46, "15": 51, "16": 56, "17": 53, "18": 41, "19": 33, "20": 23, "21": 20, "22": 17, "4": 0, "5": 17, "6": 20, "7": 33, "8": 25, "9": 15}}'::jsonb, NULL, ARRAY['Badminton court'], NULL, '05:00', '23:00') ON CONFLICT (place_id) DO UPDATE SET name = EXCLUDED.name, address = EXCLUDED.address, city = EXCLUDED.city, district = EXCLUDED