G_YFQ&cb_client=maps_sv.tactile.gps&w=224&h=298&yaw=274.80344&pitch=0&thumbfov=100"}]'::jsonb, '{"Friday": ["7 a.m.–10 p.m."], "Monday": ["7 a.m.–10 p.m."], "Saturday": ["7 a.m.–10 p.m."], "Sunday": ["7 a.m.–10 p.m."], "Thursday": ["7 a.m.–10 p.m."], "Tuesday": ["7 a.m.–10 p.m."], "Wednesday": ["7 a.m.–10 p.m."]}'::jsonb, '[{"Name": "Aditya Kandari", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUK-y6bFpyUsni-oYUw24Y5bgMsFEg0AI2ZMO1j6ygzD5Q6Ecxcgg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "Great vibes, welcoming community!\nPikaball Pickleball Court is an awesome place to play. The owner and staff are genuinely nice, friendly, and always make everyone feel welcome. They also run really fun socials with a great atmosphere, and it’s especially perfect for beginners and lower-intermediate players—super easy to jump in and improve without feeling intimidated.\n\nThe open terrace courts are a blast to play on, and you’ll definitely have fun whether you come solo or with friends. Highly recommend!", "Images": ["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1NWuBNfp3l_sItFTFGwI5bG8XaOA_ouWISKQ7hHHZDQ2-b5nLZc9GneCeklRQdOebM2drrP9zKdmq43Ni6DuLu_a-HaMmd4rzfzYxe2W3tbgE24Ashu_hvZyGUH8_08YDNz3u45M-qs5H8=k-no", "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1lNYCPdhCGrUIcxJb8hXbpDfmXuqlWfWpHn9RhIEhT0yQAj6xjxzuTNFeQhtu0azTKC-TPsIXSNikNjxzpmhiLPwzClkbEEjMCFjrbqbLPuout5F-r_wtFneYQEd-WdMD_7bEZNi6E-l9o=k-no"], "When": "2026-1-18"}, {"Name": "Maria Ahmad", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYqlph_SL8kY9U9ILMatJQ7CI-CQo1MySDUPCaJvnT2bfauZu-hQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "Great host on Reclub! We got in last minute and host was accommodating! Here got local and tourist players joining the game. It’s cheap if you join on Reclub. Court and lightning is good. Could be a little windy but overall an enjoyable play! ✨", "Images": ["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0Jo6-8jh39ZP-q4HY2NvWsbucjjpt7DKIQ9h0GcRWH8bGqMZrVD4Kl7R7UoYLphZZVK24Jn-4SfSp3W0z1rWPof9n0OTU_r-TKOkbWTDj6esUat5UQvWAUrdmlxjdaTFXihofz5csczywy=k-no"], "When": "2026-2-17"}, {"Name": "Iutt Caga", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKQHMAOG0kX4JXdDO-TVh3wVlir805Kibvqp_eOZHscb3LImg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "Vacationing in Da Nang and itchy for some pickleball. Found this open and airy rooftop Pickleball facility with 3 courts. Well lit with proper netting between courts. Friendly and welcoming staff (Dang & Vu) helped me with some drop-in games for 3 hours. Located behind the Tourane hotel on the 3/F.  Had a blast and met some other travelers and locals. Highly recommended if you are in Da Nang and want some exercises.", "Images": ["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1p8Qhm4F-9zpYCNXr4IRK0VLAxDeTK8Aq5WJBEfMbFS2zZpGBxYol715FYMp_G_UAETqhk0d2EdJLTiBsPxlPSUJBALAMyr4b_-dEBc6Ts3R-WcKHZ0CSs-xhXxiIA6A0FvaXMuCLB5lI=k-no", "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn12axUDfXtiLvjySYIwHKPWNFogHQwluaIrBaY0-i6jjADQmZCNpfmwIqgK6KkhZTeDy8m1jAb3FUN8SF_yDdCtbssWonth9w7sQqKGdica-IA-JUqaUvwMdDbGmtEvhUxcy6wrlhZBOKI=k-no", "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1Do2foyiqJ2bDxjNMwQccffOgF3waXNuLrdwlUoSPHTGLXRPT1SrnbzyDTeN28zWgLVW5FJlkSI3073OsHAJxDWvsKDJbBPkM2k6Ma-c0TjDJeJfzXP14Ro3zq4gMprBKtzB8VLR5n5XUx=k-no", "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3fnabwS1_fhxA-txYDh3WwTHP_ayJ0qTcFePqXOppsajaYMiF07DW8UIyNiYfR-yfDrg1K5kWrT2lai2GZuEpOi11hw_1vzlgFgbyB5FaGtmIafvD-klq-W9TYa6NgWVIV_6JciFmYQ5w=k-no"], "When": "2025-12-16"}, {"Name": "Kim Welling", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVKy_ghgZiJzZOkZF_BZiGMCRF1IqwZgzatcDQtYM7J3mv3BXM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "Fantastic staff. Great courts.  Shady all morning.  I showed up solo and had people to play with.  Loved it!!!", "Images": ["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1QZK3lmHvGssd_35yneupsLF_q-hiQSypNpbV3Zq9hvvsQQlzyv5EpDQco5odNTMfEmkISM3J5BbGtV1esfOcqPc4vjbbWPbY8d37SbHfkYtMN4R_rM3KdkgwVokf69DR0ScgPAuhznec=k-no", "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1ysnOOO-TMqef6CAKJe31cq_3BKqrGZNGUiHJlO9WjGHL0nJHPGVVr9Okni58mydBCvShuX4VGotN1t9CGM3rHJW1MW9n09DoZ0gA7ShJaxjgdmh6Pf8jXtQuoj_Snp_e1PQwqQSJ975mW=k-no", "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn36SMSzqLS14pdQvUvRX4oUZr2FBG7oLY8ieO1Sb18dHOMF3Kjzl5wxh_3uCpiNSdGho3DBIZliCCeCpJBkS2NtLhVeI15ftrscduS3NkcYdpVQA8UJXbbTPeM_dEKGPvsaoUXJ8PNpuAc=k-no", "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3p2K98FtFyi3_bn-uYiwgCuND_ek1Qt_G6JQiMjFChGjTWl3DKEKA3z7wUYRIHOjSZ77HFmqJWwf0twj9MldesQrDnSa8VuoWOKO7k0li7Na3cX9qrqpYVybINYWT4oPAmxeLausyd-_iY=k-no"], "When": "2026-2-28"}, {"Name": "Thanh Dinh", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI5X98VDUP5XeMzzS5sihmjaFJK-iorhXWBfddoOmxWax3jPg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "Great place to play pickleball! The courts are clean, well-maintained, and have plenty of space. The lighting is perfect for evening games, and the staff is super friendly and helpful. Highly recommend this spot for both beginners and experienced players!", "Images": ["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3daHGKuVxwie1N3QL3DmveI1WvwxkKoq5fXkNw_T4pEJW0oZkSLm5aCgfkWNQJzVDTk4-heChF4yfGUivF0DEOp_w7k1OCVg8WiuofTKGnk8RKSKnrDi-HmjxujLT1zSyTtW98c29aTJk=k-no"], "When": "2025-11-11"}, {"Name": "Keoni-jon Pasquale", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWp1_IevKfgAnRZdyUvDwBnsQaBvm2Qc9UEakx6YPzSQgNNuerS=s120-c-rp-mo-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "Pikaball is an amazing place to experience pickleball for all levels of play. My buddy Vũ works / upkeeps the place and is always down to help or jump in and play. If you’re in the Da Nang area, Pikaball is a must stop for great people and beachside rooftop vibes!", "Images": ["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1nWAAyLkF-5pwpTEl9O_wzRe9EAMzWjs-dT_ZxE0eWD5rMcxF1iNQ4zzA7Ef7n3sbY5sGgmTYJ3kBPxoZWKsI9tFHqHnipt_JhowRvVdxJBpKXO4esAqqe3EmYyS7gHJLUDbs3D_4IqWA=k-no", "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1rAjcMtyNosvt0qZZA3SbsnFerlY1GLTKLe9H-mvE0MiZ3ER4pTC-NXNuNlqpOirZgW2dcpVkkUliRzhC248MMjU_eVZpPjbstzAPVSEPA5eMS-1uMQy2evTFi-2jPBqXHZmWmdAbg5EI=k-no", "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn00AKRCOrVRt15j-jAE7FO7VSK-uQDFGsUQvt3ZlFefKVHDo-7XfQKav6t_P2fuIlN0BinJ4MkSW_S_4ds7EtbPLiYOhlulwrFzoqoYUl_xt9AmPx1cx_8Xhp0UhH2sMyzHAj10oKYDMJw=k-no"], "When": "2025-12-26"}, {"Name": "Rhea Rose Aranas Ladero", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWxU0JtCWmLi5NhyrlRYbz5284aV1pulBhNxQZZoBqVewgXNqcD=s120-c-rp-mo-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "Really love playing at Pikaball Da Nang. The court is well maintained, the view is great, and the community is very welcoming. Always good games and good vibes here. We keep coming back.", "Images": ["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3Ryx94cyiG-PC2wSttzuH9Jkbtnm1WtK-tCHIItcP9ueBXdGzxT2mUBtKoXFU0ZvHKQiPefkgMCE_cXDo26JP86VZQaGWP8I8oyXjaKih79OtoTQ_3HCyJ7Fab38LFqV2DUukpzTF2JpAo=k-no"], "When": "2026-1-26"}, {"Name": "Tyler Merry", "ProfilePicture": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUHRdC8BW_7PCyLZujfn_wz5inXl0iuBJivRaJ7Azk0kNgfnwjX-A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100", "Rating": 5, "Description": "We did a 3 hour social play here. We found it on reclub. The players and host were all very nice and play was friendly. There was a good number of players to courts so you got to play plenty.\n\nCourts are nice, it is outdoor so check the weather before going and set expectations accordingly. Wind sun and rain could all effect play, but it was all acceptable for my level.\n\nThey have a drink fridge if you want to buy a cold drink. :)", "Images": null, "When": ""}]'::jsonb, '{"Friday": {"10": 25, "11": 25, "12": 22, "13": 22, "14": 30, "15": 47, "16": 61, "17": 66, "18": 52, "19": 47, "20": 38, "21": 33, "22": 0, "23": 0, "6": 0, "7": 30, "8": 36, "9": 27}, "Monday": {"10": 19, "11": 30, "12": 38, "13": 41, "14": 50, "15": 58, "16": 77, "17": 88, "18": 77, "19": 58, "20": 47, "21": 27, "22": 0, "23": 0, "6": 0, "7": 16, "8": 16, "9": 16}, "Saturday": {"10": 41, "11": 38, "12": 27, "13": 33, "14": 41, "15": 47, "16": 52, "17": 41, "18": 41, "19": 33, "20": 36, "21": 41, "22": 0, "23": 0, "6": 0, "7": 22, "8": 27, "9": 41}, "Sunday": {"10": 41, "11": 33, "12": 27, "13": 33, "14": 41, "15": 52, "16": 66, "17": 69, "18": 69, "19": 55, "20": 41, "21": 27, "22": 0, "23": 0, "6": 0, "7": 36, "8": 47, "9": 55}, "Thursday": {"10": 22, "11": 16, "12": 8, "13": 8, "14": 13, "15": 27, "16": 52, "17": 80, "18": 100, "19": 86, "20": 61, "21": 38, "22": 0, "23": 0, "6": 0, "7": 8, "8": 13, "9": 22}, "Tuesday": {"10": 30, "11": 44, "12": 50, "13": 55, "14": 58, "15": 66, "16": 86, "17": 83, "18": 69, "19": 47, "20": 33, "21": 25, "22": 0, "23": 0, "6": 0, "7": 22, "8": 27, "9": 30}, "Wednesday": {"10": 25, "11": 27, "12": 19, "13": 19, "14": 30, "15": 44, "16": 55, "17": 52, "18": 58, "19": 50, "20": 38, "21": 33, "22": 0, "23": 0, "6": 0, "7": 22, "8": 22, "9": 27}}'::jsonb, '[{"id": "amenities", "name": "Amenities", "options": [{"name": "Gender-neutral washroom", "enabled": true}]}, {"id": "payments", "name": "Payments", "options": [{"name": "Debit cards", "enabled": true}]}, {"id": "parking", "name": "Parking", "options": [{"name": "Free parking lot", "enabled": true}, {"name": "On-site parking", "enabled": true}]}]'::jsonb, ARRAY['On-site parking', 'Debit cards', 'Gender-neutral washroom', 'Free parking lot', 'Pickleball court'], NULL, '07:00', '22:00') ON CONFLICT (place_id) DO UPDATE SET name = EXCLUDED.name, address = EXCLUDED.address, city = EXCLUDED.city, district = EXCLUDED.district, lat = EXCLUDED.lat, lng = EXCLUDED.lng, rating = EXCLUDED.rating, rating_count = EXCLUDED.rating_count, phone = EXCLUDED.phone, google_maps_url = EXCLUDED.google_maps_url, booking_url = EXCLUDED.booking_url, thumbnail_url = EXCLUDED.thumbnail_url, images = EXCLUDED.images, ope